
  The CheatList Survey - September 1992 Release

  Fill in this survey and send it back to me if you have any opinions worth
  noting.  This survey is a way for me to get feedback from you, the user.
  Just print this file out and return it, with any or all of the questions
  completed.  If you have no printer, make a hand-written copy of it.

  Complete and send to: Peter Monk - CheatList
                        142 Stephen Terrace
                        Gilberton
                        SA, 5081
                        Australia
  Thanks.

  Peter Monk (Compiler)
  1992

  ************************************************************************


